    <h1><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Compliance Overview</h1>
    <p class="help-intro">Stay compliant with IRS and state requirements.</p>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Key Compliance Areas</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Form 990</strong> - Annual IRS information return</li>
            <li><strong>State Filings</strong> - Annual report to Secretary of State</li>
            <li><strong>Charitable Solicitation</strong> - Registration for fundraising</li>
            <li><strong>Grant Reporting</strong> - Reports to grantors</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Form 990 Requirements</h2>
        <table class="help-table">
            <tr>
                <td><strong>990-N (e-Postcard)</strong></td>
                <td>Gross receipts $50,000 or less</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>990-EZ</strong></td>
                <td>Gross receipts under $200,000 AND assets under $500,000</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td><strong>990 (Full)</strong></td>
                <td>Gross receipts $200,000+ OR assets $500,000+</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p><strong>Due:</strong> 15th day of 5th month after fiscal year end (May 15 for calendar year)</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-block">
        <h2>Tennessee Requirements</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Annual Report</strong> - Due annually to Secretary of State</li>
            <li><strong>Charitable Solicitation</strong> - Registration if soliciting donations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="help-tip">
        <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <strong>Tip:</strong> Enable compliance reminders in Settings to get alerts before deadlines!
    </div>
</div>
